fields.name: FTYPE
fields.chnname: 显示类型 0不限制，1手机端，2电脑端

entities.title: MATCH_GROUP
entities.remark: 交易对组维护表，控制那些撮合进程执行那些交易对

entities.title: F_ENTRUST
entities.remark: 当前委单表，包含状态0-未成交；2-部分成交；状态的用户

fields.name: IP
fields.chnname: ip地址(未绑定IP地址的密匙有效期为90天，多个用逗号分隔)

fields.name: TYPES
fields.chnname: 权限(1-只读,2-允许交易,3-允许提现,可以多个权限,用,分隔

fields.name: SENDTYPE
fields.chnname: SMS_TEXT(1, "普通短信","SMS_TEXT"),     SMS_VOICE(2,"语音短信","SMS_VOICE"),     SMS_INTERNATIONAL(3,"国际短信","SMS_INTERNATIONAL"),     EMAIL(4,"邮件","EMAIL"),     SMS_VERIFY(5,"验证码","SMS_VERIFY")

fields.name: ACTION
fields.chnname: 普通短信:SMS_TEXT,语音短信:SMS_VOICE,国际短信:SMS_INTERNATIONAL,邮件:EMAIL,验证码:SMS_VERIFY

fields.name: IS_PLATFORM_TRANSFER_FEE
fields.chnname: 平台互转是否收取手续费，0 不收，1收

fields.name: IS_SUB_COIN
fields.chnname: 是否是从币。从币不会生成钱包，而且充提都会归集到主钱包

fields.name: USE_NEW_WAY
fields.chnname: 是否使用新的方式对接

fields.name: IOE_WHITELIST
fields.chnname: ioe售卖白名单,用户id，使用“#”号分割

fields.name: NOTICE_CHANNEL
fields.chnname: 默认1:全部通知都开启,2:开启短信,3:开启邮件

fields.name: FTYPE
fields.chnname: 充值码充值类型 0 RMB >0虚拟币ID

fields.name: TYPE
fields.chnname: 类型 1 普通 2 手气

fields.name: IS_RECEIVED
fields.chnname: 是否被领取 0 否 1 是
